      <tr>
         <td class="pbTitle">
         <h2>Step 2: Configure your User Profiles</h2>
         </td>
         <td class="pbHelp"></td>
      </tr>
   </tbody>
</table>
</div>
<div class="pbBody">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" class="setupOverview">
   <tbody>
      <tr>
         <td>If your organization supports Custom Profiles, follow the below steps to configure your User Profiles:
         <ol>
            <li>Navigate to "Setup->Administrative Setup->Manage Users->Users".</li>
            <li>Click on the "edit" link next to the User that will use Z-Billing for Salesforce.com.</li>
            <li>Find the "Profile" field and select "Read-Only Zuora Profile".</li>
            <li>Click the "Save" button.</li>
            <li>Repeat the above steps for all Users using Z-Billing for Salesforce.com application.</li>
         </ol>

         </td>
      </tr>
   </tbody>
</table>
</div>
